{"id": "ChIJocSTAH_HwoARErusHStl97E", "rating": 4.9, "userRatingCount": 5540, "displayName": {"text": "Sono Felice by Christine ✂", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJocSTAH_HwoARErusHStl97E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aSlVrbEVTbnBsWDBSa2QwaElXVEZrYUVSblNsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I got a hippie twist perm and had an amazing experience! Gina is so kind and generous and explained how to maintain the perm very clearly. I had damaged hair from a previous perm at a different salon, and she was able to restore my hair before curling it again. She also offered me yummy snacks and some refreshing barley tea! These are people who care about the health of your hair and are incredible at what they do. Well worth the money!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I got a hippie twist perm and had an amazing experience! Gina is so kind and generous and explained how to maintain the perm very clearly. I had damaged hair from a previous perm at a different salon, and she was able to restore my hair before curling it again. She also offered me yummy snacks and some refreshing barley tea! These are people who care about the health of your hair and are incredible at what they do. Well worth the money!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Elaine Qiao", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110126354813687989719/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVJ_9FCnL8lW5_qg7ar9BpOYGX48fD7RnZh2OPRLyYLSNqYuc4=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-22T05:20:20.032172050Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aSlVrbEVTbnBsWDBSa2QwaElXVEZrYUVSblNsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25aSlVrbEVTbnBsWDBSa2QwaElXVEZrYUVSblNsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77f0093c4a1:0xb1f7652b1dacbb12"}, {"name": "places/ChIJocSTAH_HwoARErusHStl97E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNNE5EaENNVzF4VFRKeVUyc3haSEIwUjJsdVNIYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Bella did amazing with my hair!! I’ve had a past problem with another salon who used thinning sears on my already thin hair and Bella fixed me right up, I asked for layers and face framing, she even taught me how to style them!!  when my hair heals and thickens back up I’m coming back to do even more!!! Thank you so much Bella love your work🏆  even was gifted a little hair roller.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Bella did amazing with my hair!! I’ve had a past problem with another salon who used thinning sears on my already thin hair and Bella fixed me right up, I asked for layers and face framing, she even taught me how to style them!!  when my hair heals and thickens back up I’m coming back to do even more!!! Thank you so much Bella love your work🏆  even was gifted a little hair roller.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Francisca Manterola", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103323434828420402136/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocISSSkhTXML4Weu2IoPvMaRJSUFFs9FXd-nex-T1aDVprC9Mw=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-22T01:31:41.529530783Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNNE5EaENNVzF4VFRKeVUyc3haSEIwUjJsdVNIYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xNNE5EaENNVzF4VFRKeVUyc3haSEIwUjJsdVNIYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77f0093c4a1:0xb1f7652b1dacbb12"}, {"name": "places/ChIJocSTAH_HwoARErusHStl97E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkbVNsWmFlSE51VFZCalJVaGZNemhaUTJRdE1tYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "2 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "The attention to detail is unmatched. Whether it’s the cut, color, or styling, everything comes out flawless and tailored perfectly to you. I especially appreciated how they explained the process and made sure my hair stayed healthy throughout.\n\nNot only are they incredibly talented, but they’re also professional, friendly, and make the whole experience enjoyable. You can tell they genuinely care about their clients and their work.\n\nIf you’re looking for someone you can trust with your hair—this is it. I wouldn’t go anywhere else. Highly recommend!\nTruly the best hair stylist in town !\n\nThank you Sophia and Christina👯‍♀️❤️🤗", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The attention to detail is unmatched. Whether it’s the cut, color, or styling, everything comes out flawless and tailored perfectly to you. I especially appreciated how they explained the process and made sure my hair stayed healthy throughout.\n\nNot only are they incredibly talented, but they’re also professional, friendly, and make the whole experience enjoyable. You can tell they genuinely care about their clients and their work.\n\nIf you’re looking for someone you can trust with your hair—this is it. I wouldn’t go anywhere else. Highly recommend!\nTruly the best hair stylist in town !\n\nThank you Sophia and Christina👯‍♀️❤️🤗", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Zoe Kanemitsu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104244677509574041238/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWmK7NwOVIGlpknHoSS-v55lkIyLc70gijY5TQuAZqKKNGm7REvbg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-04-23T23:55:18.520775709Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkbVNsWmFlSE51VFZCalJVaGZNemhaUTJRdE1tYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkbVNsWmFlSE51VFZCalJVaGZNemhaUTJRdE1tYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77f0093c4a1:0xb1f7652b1dacbb12"}, {"name": "places/ChIJocSTAH_HwoARErusHStl97E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBMFEzTTJTbFZHTjBsT016WklNRjh0YlU5T09IYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "I went in for a pink balayage + cut and was very satisfied (before picture attached). This was my first time receiving a balayage!\n\nMy hair stylist was Henry. He was very considerate, patient, and showed great attention to detail. The entire team also chipped in to clearly articulate how the colors would look and blend, as well as clear after care instructions.\n\nI can confidently say this salon truly cares about its craft and clients. Notably, Henry stayed late after closing to finish my cut and color with equal precision as when he had began. Thank you Sono Felice!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I went in for a pink balayage + cut and was very satisfied (before picture attached). This was my first time receiving a balayage!\n\nMy hair stylist was Henry. He was very considerate, patient, and showed great attention to detail. The entire team also chipped in to clearly articulate how the colors would look and blend, as well as clear after care instructions.\n\nI can confidently say this salon truly cares about its craft and clients. Notably, Henry stayed late after closing to finish my cut and color with equal precision as when he had began. Thank you Sono Felice!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Lea Hunt", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/101604660501020211167/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWFAaXdqynAdg44fsBYtFHEz1mDfWK9hte8zj9gLnFALz1znOA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-21T18:42:48.949080077Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBMFEzTTJTbFZHTjBsT016WklNRjh0YlU5T09IYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xBMFEzTTJTbFZHTjBsT016WklNRjh0YlU5T09IYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77f0093c4a1:0xb1f7652b1dacbb12"}, {"name": "places/ChIJocSTAH_HwoARErusHStl97E/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaTmEwUmhWR3gyYW5ZNVpEUmlSbloyVVhGck5rRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Was able to get a same day appointment for a women’s haircut, they seem to have a lot of availability online. The whole salon was very efficient, they have people checking you in, washing your hair, and people constantly cleaning the studio. Mia cut my hair and she did such a wonderful job, truly the best haircut I’ve ever gotten! I just wanted long layers and she captured my vision perfectly. Overall the service was high quality and so fast!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Was able to get a same day appointment for a women’s haircut, they seem to have a lot of availability online. The whole salon was very efficient, they have people checking you in, washing your hair, and people constantly cleaning the studio. Mia cut my hair and she did such a wonderful job, truly the best haircut I’ve ever gotten! I just wanted long layers and she captured my vision perfectly. Overall the service was high quality and so fast!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Erin Lee", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110141511721126909072/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWwMH74NEDuR14P4z4pOf0YIUKYOKcYL7DvxduzOXvJtPBOX_A8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-06T22:44:27.221964663Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaTmEwUmhWR3gyYW5ZNVpEUmlSbloyVVhGck5rRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2xaTmEwUmhWR3gyYW5ZNVpEUmlSbloyVVhGck5rRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2c77f0093c4a1:0xb1f7652b1dacbb12"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJocSTAH_HwoARErusHStl97E/photos/AWCwydjhAzdrTfkfSv0IlR2u4hmw347d4SUTtHbRV_JAU0DCCbZ